name: Raggae Plant
description: This monster loves a certain kind of music very much.

name: Romper Wall
description: It's so friendly that often tries to take too much care of humans.

name: Obelisk
description: It is rather active, so it cannot be used as a stone wall.

name: Jura Wall
description: Noodles, which are made by using its moist body, are tasty.

name: Blue Sponge
description: You are guaranteed a good night's sleep if you sleep on it.

name: Furred Wall
description: Though it has fluffy hair, its body is hard.

name: Ivory Wall
description: It has the pattern of God that is embossed on its body.

name: Sandy
description: Its conspicuous figure is easy to spot even if it has escaped.

name: Ice Candy
description: During summer, its body is cool and comfortable to lie on.

name: New Leaf
description: It'll be filled with energy when half of its body is burried.

name: Monol
description: It will separate into pieces to cushion against enemy's attacks.

name: Soboros
description: It has eyes unlike other Monol and can see its enemy.

name: Asphaltum
description: Ants try to make colonies in it, but it is impossible.

name: Galaxy
description: This monster relates to the Sky monster in the FIMBA area.

name: Dominos
description: These monsters like to gather and form a line.

name: Scribble
description: This monster is rarely found in the IMa area.

name: Rock Ape
description: It is a lazy monster and sits as still as a stone statue.

name: Gibberer
description: Female trainers try not to teach it some kind of techniques.

name: Bossy
description: Though it is one of the laziest monsters, it is quite capable.

name: Tropical Ape
description: This monster sprays a scent that decreases fighting spirit.

name: Ape
description: There are many legends regarding this one's laziness.

name: Gold Dust
description: It seems to be decadent, but it is actually a hard worker.

name: Red Worm
description: It may emerge as a beautiful monster once in a long while.

name: Rock Worm
description: It has beautiful eyes, but they do not work well in the light.

name: Scaled Worm
description: It hides its legs and uses them only for quick movement.

name: Drill Tusk
description: Its drill-like tusks can break even hard rocks into pieces.

name: Corone
description: A chocolate-filled sweet pastry is named after this one.

name: Mask Worm
description: Though it is a descendant from God, it is not all that tough.

name: Eye Worm
description: It has four fake eyes, and single real eye is usually hidden in its forehead.

name: Jelly Worm
description: Its flabby body cushions against its enemy's attack.

name: Flower Worm
description: The contrast of its red body and blue eyes is very beautiful.

name: Black Worm
description: This monster is used to carry heavy objects.

name: Worm
description: Its abilities are all in balance and it has no weak points.

name: Purple Worm
description: It frightens its enemies with its multitude of shiny eyes.

name: Express Worm
description: None can compete with its speed as long as it is on its line.

name: Ripper
description: Its IQ is high, but it often mistakes itself for a human.

name: Trident
description: It likes to kill its enemies with one deadly attack.

name: Stinger
description: It always holds its tongue out to cool its body temperature.

name: Striker
description: Its obedient character is rare for the Naga species.

name: Edgehog
description: It is descended from the Hare species, but it is very violent.

name: Bazula
description: It is very careful and is rarely caught off guard.

name: Cyclops
description: It is so clever that it often disagrees with its trainer.

name: Aqua Cutter
description: It is a Jell monster that is shaped in the form of Naga.

name: Jungler
description: It hides in the forest and hunts animals.

name: Crimson Eyed
description: It likes to damage its enemies little by little.

name: Earth Keeper
description: It won't forgive anyone, even humans, that destroy nature.

name: Naga
description: This one's cruel fighting style horrifies other monsters.

name: Time Noise
description: The secret goal that this one has is to obtain immortality.

name: Magma Heart
description: It will immediarely attack whoever invades its territory.

name: Sniper
description: This monster is feared as the dominater of the Mandy Desert.

name: Sand Golem
description: It will not forgive anyone who breaks its quiet living.

name: Wild Saurian
description: It is an active Zuum-type monster that has become winld.

name: Silver Face
description: It has escaped from its trainer because of its hard training.

name: Kamui
description: It escaped being executed for killing humans.

name: Bloody Eye
description: Its unique red eyes have caused it to be put on public display.

name: Crescent
description: An evil spirit is dwelling in it because of a forbidden drink.

name: Zilla King
description: It was awakened from an ancient sleep by a major earthquake.

name: Blue Phoenix
description: Unlike other Phoenix monsters, it is very violent.

name: Bighand
description: This kind of monsters are considered to be extinct.

name: Mad Gaboo
description: A tool to make it obey is buried in its forehead.

name: Burning Wall
description: This one escaped from its trainer while its stable was on fire.

name: King Ape
description: This monster is feared as the dominater of the Parepare Jungle.

name: Punisher
description: It is said that it was actually raised by another monster.

name: White Suezo
description: It was raised very carefully because of its pure white body.

name: White Mocchi
description: It has changed the color of its skin in order to be conspicuous.
